#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:209
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC1_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Who even were these guys? You blew them all to pieces by baiting them with scrap, and yet, you have a feeling this is not over yet... Perhaps there's more of them somewhere else...\n"
"\t\t\tWhile searching through the remains of the ship, you find a dying member of its crew, clutching an intact weapon it seemingly stripped from right from the hull. It seems like they're nibbling on it.\n"
"\t\t\tYou can snatch the weapon from them, take them both with you, or leave them to die."

