msgstr "Attempt to sneak away from the Scrapper."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2268
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ADAMANTINE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You manage to leave succesfully, with the opportunity of doing something on-"
"board."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2270
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ADAMANTINE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2274
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ADAMANTINE\"]/choice[@req=\"pilot\"]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2282
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ADAMANTINE_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The adamantine ship has been defeated.\n"
"\t\t\tWhile searching through the remains of the ship, you find a dying member of its crew, clutching an intact weapon it seemingly stripped from right from the hull. It seems like they're nibbling on it.\n"
"\t\t\tYou can snatch the weapon from them, take them both with you, or leave them to die."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2290
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ADAMANTINE_DESTROY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Snatch the weapon."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2292
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ADAMANTINE_DESTROY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You chose to take the functional weapon, leaving the crew member to its "
"fate."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2297
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ADAMANTINE_DESTROY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Allow the crew member to eat the weapon."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2299
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ADAMANTINE_DESTROY\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You promise the scrapper additional scrap for work and a home onboard a non-"
"destroyed ship. After beaming aboard, they quickly finish the weapon, "
"revitalizing themselves."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2304
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ADAMANTINE_DESTROY\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Spend some extra time salvaging."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2306
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ADAMANTINE_DESTROY\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You instead spend some extra time salvaging and beam away without looking back.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\tThe wounded scrapper watches you beam away, who knows if it will live or die floating forever, lost in space wreckage. How rude."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2326
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_SKIP\"]/text"
msgstr "How the hell did you do that."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2333
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your systems go on high alert as your arrival is met with a massive Lanius "
"ship, its weapons raised and charging!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2336
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "I am waiting."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2337
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "We are finished."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2338
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip"
msgstr "I am waiting."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2349
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "No time to prepare!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2360
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"The Lanius' offensive systems all power down in an instant, and you're met with a hail. On screen comes a featureless Lanius, covered by a shimmering prismatic bubble. \n"
"\"Apologies, I'm merely fascinated by first impressions.\" Its body flexes in manner similar to chuckling, as it logs something into its console."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2363
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "What? You did all that just to get a reaction out of me?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2365
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"As best as you can tell, a bemused expression encroaches the lanius' lack of a face. \"To a degree... yes, though the exact reasons are a touch more esoteric...\" It paces around their helm for a moment, before jerking their attention back to you.\n"
"\"Right, my manners, I've misplaced them.\" They give a small bow before standing upright, arms spread wide in an assumedly welcoming gesture. \"I am The Architect, creator and caretaker of the Scrappers.\" Their arms fall to their sides, posture relaxing. \n"
"\"They are as aged as the Lanius, and have grown quite varied across the Multiverse.\" A fleet of Scrapper Cruisers blip into view, behind the Architect's."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2369
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "So... why am I here?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2371
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Succinctly, your exceptional capabilities. Your victories against my older"
" creations are no small feat, even with the assistance of compatriots.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2373
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Do you mean the Trash Compactor?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2375
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Indeed. My more recent creations, the Elemental Scrappers, were an "
"escalation worth testing against you. Granted, most are overly narrow in "
"scope, yet I see such merit in perfecting a purpose. What do you see in "
"them?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2377
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Elegance, if I had to put it into one word."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2379
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They bask in the moment, proud of such high praise for their work. \"You "
"elate me so, thank you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2381
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2387
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Most are good, but some could definitely do with some work."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2389
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "\"I appreciate the earnesty, as perfection does not come without error.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2391
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2397
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "I've seen better."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2399
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "\"... Duly noted...\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2401
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CONTINUE\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2433
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Righting themselves, the Architect refocuses on you once more. \"In any "
"case, I've one more design of my creation in need of a proper test. Yes, "
"there is indeed a reward awaiting you, should you succeed. Would you honor "
"me so?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2435
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Agree."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2437
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Which pairing intrigues you most?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2439
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Adamantine + Golden."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2441
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Architect's ship moves away to a safer distance and one of the Scrapper "
