#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2475
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2483
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Decline."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2485
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You're met with a long pause, and a creeping sense of disappointment. A low "
"nod escapes the Architect. \"Very well. That will be the end of our "
"interactions.\" Their ship jumps away, the fleet of Scrappers soon following"
" after."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2488
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2492
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_CHOICE\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2504
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_MERGED_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the Scrapper splits into debris, the Architect's vessel emerges. \"A "
"wonderfully executed battle, congratulations. As promised, your reward.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2506
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_MERGED_DESTROY\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "That's it? Just one last fight and we're done?"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2508
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_MERGED_DESTROY\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Architect pauses in their tracks, facing you once more. A suggestion of confusion upon their blank visage is met with an inquisitively raised hand. \"I had not expected such gumption from you, yet perhaps that much should have been readily apparent. Your attempts to even reach me in such a way is already extraordinary on its own...\" \n"
"They mumble to themselves, pacing back and forth as they ponder your response. All at once, it dawns on them.\n"
"\"Ah. You desire challenge, do you not? And perhaps further reward for such monumental effort?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2512
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_MERGED_DESTROY\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Send me your strongest."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2516
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_MERGED_DESTROY\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"They give that same chuckle-like gesture, stance postured for dramatics. \"I shall do you one better. Me. I am to be your final opponent, with no quarter given.\" They relax, just a touch. \"I have never truly tested my own design's efficacy. This would be a grand experiment for both of us. I trust you will have no difficulty finding me once more. I'll be waiting.\" \n"
"The Architect's ship jumps away. Their vessel leaves a quickly fading shimmer in the space it once occupied."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2521
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_MERGED_DESTROY\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "On second thought, I'm good."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2524
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_MERGED_DESTROY\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The Architect nods. \"Very well. You've performed more than admirably so "
"far. I shant take more of your time. I wish you well with your mission.\" "
"The Architect's ship jumps away. Their vessel leaves a quickly fading "
"shimmer in the space it once occupied."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2543
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "I am waiting."

