msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Your arrival is met with a hail from the Architect. \"Greetings. Are you "
"prepared?\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2572
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr "I am waiting."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2573
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/beaconType/visitedTooltip"
msgstr "We are finished."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2574
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/beaconType/undiscoveredTooltip"
msgstr "I am waiting."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2578
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Yes."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2580
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Let us begin, then.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2590
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2596
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "No."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2598
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "\"Another time, then.\" They jump away."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2601
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Do something onboard the ship."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2605
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$/dummyroot/FTL/event[@name=\"ENCOUNTER_TC_ZOG_FIGHT_YES\"]/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Do nothing."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2673
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As the Architect's ship shatters into countless shards, you hear them teleport beside you. \"Wonderful! Truly, wonderfully done! I could not execute a better performance myself.\" You catch them staring out towards the wreckage of their cruiser. \n"
"\"Much as I adored my design, its destruction only shows its imperfection. Now I've the perfect opportunity to perfect it.\" You catch what might be a smile on their faceless face. They shake their head a touch, turning to you.\n"
"\"Right, your reward! I would hope that you find the selections on offer sufficient for your purposes. Though, if you'd kindly, only take one.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2680
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Omega Amalgam Flak."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2682
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"It's a miracle this weapon doesn't tear itself apart while firing. If "
"memory serves me, its constructed of... platinum, iridium, and osmium, as "
"you might call them.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2685
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2691
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Midnight Prismatic Flak."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2693
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Many disparate ideas fueled this weapon, and I simply couldn't decide on "
"just one.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2696
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2702
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Elemental Toggle Flak."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2704
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"\"The Toggle Flak is already a joy to behold, yet I saw to it that it should"
" reach even higher potentials.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2707
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TC_ZOG_DESTROY\"]/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:2713
