"us? What about our rivalry, the most legendary rivalry to ever exist, and "
"you found ANOTHER me? I thought we had something special, we've fought each "
"other so many times, had so many amazing moments and you... you... you cheat"
" on me!\" Leah slams her fist down onto the table and leaps from her seat. "
"\"No more games captain, our rivalry is over, and only one of us is going to"
" make it out of here alive. Ooh, but what if we both died at the same time, "
"wouldn't that make for such a cool and epic mo-\" You close communications "
"and begin to charge your weapons."

